<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <!-- The above 3 meta tags *must* come first in the head; any other head content must come *after* these tags -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-BVYiiSIFeK1dGmJRAkycuHAHRg32OmUcww7on3RYdg4Va+PmSTsz/K68vbdEjh4u" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.11.0/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.2.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0-beta.2/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-alpBpkh1PFOepccYVYDB4do5UnbKysX5WZXm3XxPqe5iKTfUKjNkCk9SaVuEZflJ" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

  </head>

  <body>

    {{>header}}

    <!-- Main jumbotron for a primary marketing message or call to action -->
    <div class="jumbotron">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Search Your Restaurants in Hoboken</h2>
        <p>This is a template for a simple marketing or informational website. </p>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="smallContainer">
                <img src="" class="bodyImage">
                <h3><a class="title" href="#">Cuisine</a></h3>
                <p>This is a template for a simple marketing or informational website.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="smallContainer">
                <img src="" class="bodyImage">
                <h3><a class="title" href="/restaurants/rating">Rating</a></h3>
                <p>This is a template for a simple marketing or informational website. </p>
            </div>

            <div class="smallContainer">
                <img src="" class="bodyImage">
                <h3><a class="title" href="#">Nearby</a></h3>
                <p>This is a template for a simple marketing or informational website. </p>
            </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <div class="row" >
          {{#each all}}
           <div class="col-md-4">
              <h2>{{this.R_name}}</h2>
              <p>{{this.R_href}}</p>
              <p>Donec id elit non mi porta gravida at eget metus. Fusce dapibus, tellus ac cursus commodo, tortor mauris condimentum nibh, ut fermentum massa justo sit amet risus. Etiam porta sem malesuada magna mollis euismod. Donec sed odio dui. </p>
              <a class="btn btn-default" href="/restaurants/{{this._id}}" role="button">View details &raquo;</a>   
           </div>
          {{/each}}    
      </div>   
      <hr>

      {{>footer}} 
    </div> 

  </body>
</html>